msgctxt "0000"
msgid ""
"Press <1.ic> to deflect an attack\n"
"with your shield right before it\n"
"lands for a <2.se_co>Perfect Guard<3.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"Jump out of the way of an\n"
"attack at the last moment to\n"
"execute a <1.se_co>Perfect Dodge<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: icon
#. 2: icon
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"To shield surf, jump (<1.ic>) while\n"
"holding a shield, and then\n"
"press <2.ic> while in the air."
msgstr ""

