msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"Hit an enemy's head with an\n"
"arrow to perform a <1.se_co><2.se_co>Critical Hit<3.se_co><4.re_co>\n"
"that deals 2x damage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"If your Stamina Wheel runs out,\n"
"you'll be too tired to do certain\n"
"actions until it fills up again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"The temperature is getting\n"
"dangerously low. Find warmth\n"
"soon or you'll take damage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"The temperature is getting\n"
"very high. Find a way to cool\n"
"down or you'll take damage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"Sneak up on an enemy and\n"
"unleash a melee attack to do\n"
"some major damage."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"Any attack that causes your\n"
"weapon to break becomes a\n"
"<1.se_co>Critical Hit<2.re_co>, dealing 2x damage."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"Throw a weapon at an enemy to\n"
"perform a <1.se_co>Critical Hit<2.re_co>, dealing\n"
"twice the weapon damage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"The very air around you is\n"
"burning. You'll take damage\n"
"if you stay here any longer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"Vertical surfaces become slick\n"
"with water when it rains, making\n"
"climbing more difficult."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"Wooden weapons or\n"
"shields will catch fire if\n"
"equipped in this area."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"Crouching increases your\n"
"<1.se_co>stealth<2.re_co>, making it easier to\n"
"sneak up on foes and animals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"You can't sand-seal surf\n"
"without a shield."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid ""
"Wolf Link will guide you\n"
"to locations that trigger\n"
"your Sheikah Sensor."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"Check a meal's ingredients by\n"
"selecting it from your inventory\n"
"and then selecting <1.se_co>Recipe<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"Electrical attacks can shock\n"
"you, causing you to drop the\n"
"<1.se_co>weapon <2.re_co>you're holding."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"The air has become very <1.se_co>cold<2.re_co>.\n"
"You'll take damage even with\n"
"your current food and clothes."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"The air has become very <1.se_co>hot<2.re_co>.\n"
"You'll take damage even with\n"
"your current food and clothes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"The air itself burns. Your current\n"
"clothes and food won't protect\n"
"you from taking damage."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "0023"
msgid ""
"You can manipulate certain\n"
"aspects of the Divine Beast\n"
"from the <1.se_co>Map Screen<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

